SHARING THE APP 
------------------------
to share, you need to use a DOCKER REGISTRY
Docker hub is the default registry 

Create a repo 
> docker hub > login > repositories > create repository > fill in blanks > create 

$ docker push perryr16/getting-started:tagname

check it 
    $ docker image ls 
        # perryr16/getting-started isnt there ...
login to change the name 
    $ docker login -u perryr16 
change the tag 
    $ docker tag getting-started perryr16/getting-started
    $ docker image ls 
push it 
    $ docker push perryr16/getting-started

can play with it at labs.play-with-docker.com